title: Increasing share of emissions going to ALCX holders
body:
Yesterday, I posted a proposal of a new emissions split on the ALCX forum, where I explain my rationale on why I think we need to increase the share of emissions going to ALCX holders.

https://forum.alchemix.fi/public/d/16-discussion-increasing-share-of-emissions-going-to-alcx-holders/43

After hearing the feedback of the community through discussions and a discord poll, I would like to propose the following split which I think represents the community's rough consensus.

ETH-ALCX sushi pool : 60%
ALCX-only staking : 20%
3CRV-alUSD pool : 18%
alUSD pool : 2%

Note that this is the split that got the most votes on the discord poll.

Please signal if you support this proposal or not.
